msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/date"
msgid "November 23rd, 1943 - Armeegruppe 35/46."
msgstr "23 de noviembre de 1943 - Armeegruppe 35/46."

#, boost-format
msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/defence_progress"
msgid "Enemy wave %1% out of 10 underway!"
msgstr "¡Oleada enemiga %1% de 10 en camino!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/name"
msgid "In Spite of Everything"
msgstr "Pese a todo"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/name_big"
msgid "In Spite of Everything"
msgstr "Pese a todo"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/assistant/skip"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/1"
msgid ""
"Soldiers! The enemy is about to assault this position in great numbers. "
"Today we have to stand our ground! The Wotan line must stop the bolsheviks "
"right here."
msgstr "¡Soldados! El enemigo está a punto de asaltar nuestra posición con un gran número de tropas. ¡Hoy tenemos que proteger lo que es nuestro! ¡Que la línea Wotan demuestre su valía ante los bolchevique!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/10"
msgid ""
"They must be preparing for another major assault. Now that they are familiar "
"with our positions, they'll be attempting to mash us to pieces! "
msgstr "Seguramente estén organizando otro asalto. Ahora que conocen nuestra ubicación, ¡es probable que intenten hacernos añicos! "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/11"
msgid ""
"Use this time to build new defensive positions! and lay more mines! Expect "
"the soviets to bombard the current ones!"
msgstr "¡Aprovecha para formar nuevas posiciones defensivas y plantar más minas! ¡Intuyo que los soviéticos bombardearán nuestra posición actual!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/12"
msgid ""
"Excellent work soldiers. Our forward observers have spotted the enemy tank "
"forces halting their offensive. Fend off their remaining infantry! This is "
"our last stand! Make the Reich proud!"
msgstr "Bien hecho, soldados. Nuestros observadores han avistado cómo los tanques enemigos cesaban el ataque. ¡Acaba con los soldados de infantería supervivientes! ¡A resistir, por el Reich!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/13"
msgid ""
"Once more you have proven your tactical leadership Herr Leutnant. I'm proud "
"to be serving by your side."
msgstr "Has vuelto a demostrar tu talento táctico, Herr Leutnant. Es un honor combatir a tu lado."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/14"
msgid "All the troops have been lost! The enemy has obliterated your men!"
msgstr "¡Hemos perdido a todas nuestras tropas! ¡El enemigo ha arrasado con tu ejército!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/15"
msgid ""
"The Soviets have breached the industrial area! Our key position has been "
"completely overrun!"
msgstr "¡Los soviéticos han irrumpido en la zona industrial! ¡Nos han arrebatado la posición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/16"
msgid ""
"The enemy has set foot in the industrial area! You need to drive them out of "
"there immediately, that's an order!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo se ha adentrado en la zona industrial! Expúlsalos cuanto antes, ¡es una orden!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/17"
msgid ""
"Russians in the factory facilities! Herr Leutnant, drive them out of there "
"now! Or we're lost!"
msgstr "¡Hay rusos en las instalaciones de la fábrica! Herr Leutnant, ¡sácalos de ahí o nos podemos dar por muertos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/18"
msgid ""
"The enemy has entered our industrial position! Eliminate them as the highest "
"priority! If more of them enter the premises, we're done!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo ha entrado en nuestra posición industrial! Tu prioridad es acabar con ellos porque como entren más unidades a las premisas, ¡estamos muertos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/2"
msgid ""
"Your task is to hold this industrial position at all costs. Expect attacks "
"from all sides! Luckily the poor weather keeps enemy attack aircraft "
"grounded. No reinforcements are available, but we have a solid line of "
"defence at your disposal. You are our only hope in stopping the red tide!"
msgstr "Tu objetivo es mantener la posición industrial cueste lo que cueste, pero ¡ten en cuenta que atacarán por todos lados! Por suerte, gracias al mal tiempo no nos pueden atacar por aire. Por otro lado, aunque no depongamos de refuerzos, nuestra línea defensiva es bastante sólida. ¡Eres la última esperanza del Reich, acaba con los rojos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/3"
msgid "Armored vehicles are expected from the south..."
msgstr "Esperamos la llegada de vehículos blindados procedentes del sur..."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/4"
msgid ""
"Enemy infantry regiments crossed the Dnieper and are expected to attack us "
"from the north... we don't know how much longer it will take for them to "
"build pontoon crossings and deploy armored divisions from this sector..."
msgstr "Varios regimientos de infantería han cruzado el Dniéper y pretenden atacarnos por el norte... Desconocemos cuánto tiempo tardarán en construir un puente de pontones y desplegar divisiones blindadas desde ese sector..."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/5"
msgid ""
"We also anticipate that Ivan will attempt to break through at the village. "
"Grenadiers with short range weaponry have been deployed there for close "
"quarters combat..."
msgstr "Además, creemos que Ivan tratará de irrumpir en la aldea. Se han desplegado granaderos de corta distancia para combatir de cerca..."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/6"
msgid ""
"You have some time to prepare the defences before the arrival of the first "
"enemy scouts. Dig foxholes, position your men and lay down the mines from "
"the crates by the dispersal area."
msgstr "Aprovecha que no han llegado todavía exploradores enemigos para preparar las defensas. Cava hoyos, traslada a tus soldados e instala las minas que contienen las cajas ubicadas en la zona de dispersión."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/7"
msgid ""
"The enemy is almost here. Man your positions! If we can hold until nightfall "
"the enemy may call off their assault!"
msgstr "Ya casi ha llegado el enemigo, ¡refuerza las posiciones! Si aguantamos hasta el anochecer, ¡puede que el enemigo se retire!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/8"
msgid ""
"That was not much... I believe we are about to face the true grunt of the "
"enemy attack. Get ready to defend the southern flank!"
msgstr "No ha sido para tanto... Es posible que todavía no nos hayan atacado con todo. ¡Prepárate para defender el flanco sur!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/9"
msgid ""
"The Soviets have slowed down their pace. They must be preparing for a "
"decisive blow! Use this valuable time to resupply and reinforce the defences!"
msgstr "Los soviéticos han reducido el ritmo, ¡seguramente pretendan asestarnos un golpe final! ¡Aprovecha para reabastecer y reforzar las defensas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/artillery"
msgid ""
"The enemy has deployed heavy artillery on the northwest. They're trying to "
"bombard us from afar!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo ha desplegado su artillería pesada al noroeste! ¡Quieren bombardearnos a distancia!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/mortars1"
msgid "The soviets are deploying mortars on the north!"
msgstr "¡Los soviéticos están desplegando morteros al norte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/mortars2"
msgid "Enemy mortars spotted in the south! They're planning to bomb us out!"
msgstr "¡Morteros enemigos en el sur! ¡Nos quieren bombardear!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/n_generic1"
msgid "The bolsheviks are coming from the north!"
msgstr "¡Los bolcheviques vuelven del norte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/n_generic2"
msgid "Ivan is assaulting our northern flank!"
msgstr "¡Ivan está invadiendo el flanco al norte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/n_inf"
msgid ""
"The Soviet infantry has arrived to our northern positions! We're now "
"fighting on 2 fronts! "
msgstr "¡Han llegado tropas de infantería soviéticas a nuestras posiciones al norte! ¡Estamos combatiendo en 2 frentes! "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/nw_generic1"
msgid "Soviet column approaching us from the northwest! On the road!"
msgstr "¡Se aproxima una columna soviética por el noroeste! ¡Por carretera!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/nw_generic2"
msgid ""
"Ivan has been spotted in the north west. They're coming along the mud road."
msgstr "Hemos ubicado a Ivan al noroeste. Se aproximan a nosotros por el camino de barro."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/s_generic1"
msgid "Soviets spotted near the southern road! They're coming this way!"
msgstr "¡Hemos visto soviéticos cerca de la carretera al sur! ¡Vienen por aquí!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/s_generic2"
msgid "Enemy troops coming from the south, from the main road!"
msgstr "¡Se acercan tropas enemigas por la carretera principal ubicada al sur!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/s_tanks"
msgid "Enemy tank column coming from the south on the road!"
msgstr "¡Se aproxima una columna de tanques enemiga por la carretera al sur!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/se2_generic1"
msgid "Soviets coming from the south!"
msgstr "¡Se acercan soviéticos por el sur!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/se2_generic2"
msgid "The enemy is approaching from the south!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo se acerca por el sur!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/se_generic1"
msgid "The enemy is approaching from the south east! Hold them back!"
msgstr "¡Se acercan enemigos por el sureste! ¡Que no avancen!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/se_generic2"
msgid "Soviet wave coming from the south east! "
msgstr "¡Se acerca una oleada soviética por el sureste! "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/se_scouts"
msgid "The Bolsheviks scouts are coming from the south east!"
msgstr "¡Se aproximan exploradores bolcheviques por el sureste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/sw_generic1"
msgid "Enemy infantry storming the positions on the south west!"
msgstr "¡La infantería enemiga está asaltando nuestras posiciones al suroeste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/officer/sw_generic2"
msgid "The soviets are attempting to breach our positions in the south west!"
msgstr "¡Los soviéticos están intentando irrumpir en nuestras posiciones al suroeste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/narrator/soldier/1"
msgid "Herr Leutnant, it seems the soviet stopped pressing us further!"
msgstr "Herr Leutnant, ¡parece que los rusos han dejado de presionar!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"The onslaught continued and the Wehrmacht commited all their strength and "
"courage into withstanding the red wave. In Ukraine, the tenacious Soviet \n"
"forces continued overwhelming the unfinished Wotan line with brute force. "
"Whatever fortifications had been built along the Dnieper were rather sub- "
"par, \n"
"as both materials and labour had been insufficient to build a position "
"strong enough to withstand the might of the red army. Nevertheless, in some "
"places \n"
"the Germans held the line until well into 1944. Surrounded, undergunned and "
"in spite of all the odds, the Panther-Wotan line bought precious time for "
"the \n"
"Wehrmacht, for more solid attempts to stop the avalanche of the Soviets and "
"attepmt to tilt the balance of the eastern front once more..."
msgstr "La masacre no cesó y la Wehrmacht derramó sangre y sudor para repeler la ola bolchevique. En Ucrania, las tropas \nsoviéticas siguieron atormentando a base de fuerza bruta la inacabada línea de Wotan. Todas las fortificaciones que habían sido erigidas junto al Dniéper carecían de solidez, \npues los materiales y la mano de obra empleadas no eran suficientes para repeler el potencial del ejército rojo. Aun así, los alemanes lograron \nmantener la línea en algunas secciones hasta 1944. Rodeados, sin escapatoria y pese a todo pronóstico, la línea de Panther-Wotan supuso un tiempo muy valioso para la \nWehrmacht, que consiguieron repeler la avalancha soviética y remontar posiciones en el frente oriental..."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"Since you were unable to stop the red tide here, the red army can now march "
"west unopposed. They will leave army group centre in complete disarray, \n"
"and will be able to reach Warsaw before summer. A year from now, still in "
"1944, Berlin will fall to the allies."
msgstr "No has podido detener la marea roja y ahora campan por el oeste a sus anchas. El Ejército Rojo sembrará el caos en el Grupo de Ejércitos Centro, \npor lo que llegarán a Varsovia antes del verano. En un año, todavía en 1944, los aliados someterán Berlín."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/place"
msgid "West of Gomel, Kharkov Oblast."
msgstr "Oeste de Gomel, Óblast de Járkov."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/skip"
msgid "Skip preparation phase"
msgstr "Omitir fase de preparación"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/story"
msgid "The Germans have been constructing defenses along the west bank of the Dnieper river in an attempt to stop the Red Army's advance. But the Soviets arrive earlier than expected."
msgstr "Los alemanes han organizado posiciones defensivas junto al banco occidental del Dniéper con el fin de detener el avance del Ejército Rojo. El problema: los soviéticos han llegado antes de lo esperado."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/task1"
msgid "Hold the industrial position at all costs!"
msgstr "¡Defiende la posición industrial cueste lo que cueste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/task2"
msgid "Prepare the defences"
msgstr "Prepara las defensas"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/task3"
msgid "Eliminate any remaining Soviet troops!"
msgstr "¡Elimina las tropas soviéticas que faltan!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/timer1"
msgid "Prepare defences!"
msgstr "¡Prepara las defensas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1943_11_wotan/timer2"
msgid "Time until the next wave:"
msgstr "Tiempo hasta la próxima oleada:"
